00:08:54.740 --> 00:08:55.780
Si me sellan hoy,

00:08:56.180 --> 00:08:57.380
será mi liberación.

00:08:58.940 --> 00:09:00.060
Es increíble que

00:09:01.020 --> 00:09:02.580
